[2]
仕様書:
= [DEL[[[RFC 1630]] ([[IETF]] [[情報提供]])]] <urn:ietf:rfc:1630>
= [DEL[[[RFC 1738]] ([[IETF]] [[提案標準]])]] <urn:ietf:rfc:1738>
= [[RFC 4266]] [CITE@@en[The gopher URI Scheme]] ([[IETF]] [[提案標準]]) <urn:ietf:rfc:4266>
d11 5
a15 3
